Package it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service

Provides classes defining the services that can be provided by an actor space service provider.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Service
    The Service interface defines a service that an actor space can provide.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompositeService
    The CompositeService abstract class provides a partial implementation of a composite service (i.e., a service what tasks are performed through the cooperation of some different services) that an actor space can provide.
    SimpleService
    The SimpleService abstract class provides a partial implementation of a service that an actor space can provide.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Scope
    The Scope enumeration defines where a service acts.
